<div class="head1"><a name="mrkt">Carla Raffo</a></div>
<span class="contentText"><i>Vice President, Marketing, Europe, Middle East and Africa (EMEA)</i>
<p />


Carla Raffo joined Gartner in her present role in July 2002, with more than twenty years' experience in marketing management. Her responsibilities include database marketing, internal marketing and international public relations management, throughout the region.
<p />


Prior to Gartner, Carla was marketing director for the Oracle Partner Network, EMEA, Oracle Corporation and was responsible for programme, brand and operations. 
<p />

Previously, she was director of marketing for PictureTel, EMEA, where she managed channel, product, brand marketing and communications. Carla was also part of the initial European Claris team, heading the marketing and launch of the new brand and application software across EMEA.
<p />

Carla began her career in IT at Wang Laboratories as a product specialist, later becoming a corporate account sales executive.
