<div class="head1"><a name="sales">Alister Christopher</a></div>
<span class="contentText"><i>Group Vice President, Sales, Europe, Middle East and Africa (EMEA)</i>
<p />


Alister Christopher joined Gartner in 1992 and has more than twenty years' experience working in the information technology industry. 
<p />


Alister has held a variety of sales and managerial positions during his Gartner career. Having previously been responsible for the creation and development of the EMEA Inside Sales organisation, he spent two years in the United States, managing North American Inside Sales' development.
<p />


In August 2001 Alister became Group Vice President of EMEA Sales, overseeing EMEA Sales management, Sales and Client Operations and Worldwide Sales.
<p />


Prior to joining Gartner, Alister held sales management positions with ICL U.K. Limited. 
