<div class="head1"><a name="fin">Roy Benbow</a></div>
<span class="contentText"><i>Chief Financial Officer, Europe, Middle East and Africa (EMEA)</i>
<p />

Roy Benbow joined Gartner in January 2000. As chief financial officer (CFO), his role primarily involves managing regional finance, administration, infrastructure and planning operations. He is responsible for the effective management and continued development of the Corporate Services, Finance, Financial Planning and Workplace Management departments within EMEA.
<p />


Prior to Gartner, Roy worked for StorageTek for more than 20 years and was the CFO for EMEA during his final five years.
