<div class="head1"><a name="human">Alan Miller</a></div>
<span class="contentText"><i>Vice President, Human Resources, Europe, Middle East and Africa (EMEA) </i>
<p />


Alan Miller joined Gartner in July 2002 as head of EMEA human resources, including corporate services and HR management. He will continue to develop and enhance the strong Gartner focus on professional support and guidance for the lines of business and countries throughout the region.
<p />

Prior to Gartner, Alan was vice president of European HR for Level 3 Communications. He was responsible for all HR activities, including training, development, recruitment and compensation. Alan also became director of HR for StorageTek, having previously had several years' senior-level experience in strategic business and general HR management roles within the company.
